---
---

<section class="pt-4 pb-8 md:pt-8 md:pb-16 bg-[#FCFAF7] border-b border-[#F1EBE4]">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-8 md:mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif mb-3 text-[#544A40] leading-normal px-2">
                子どもも大人も、無理なく始められるピアノレッスン
            </h2>
            <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-[#A88B58] text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-[0.2em] font-serif uppercase"
            >
                <div class="h-[1px] w-6 bg-[#A88B58]/30"></div>
                Lessons for All Ages & Levels
                <div class="h-[1px] w-6 bg-[#A88B58]/30"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6 lg:gap-8">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#E8E2D9] shadow-sm flex flex-col md:items-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#A88B58]/30">
                <div class="flex items-center md:flex-col md:text-center gap-3 mb-3 md:mb-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#A88B58]/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#A88B58] flex-shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-[#544A40] font-serif md:mt-2">子どもから大人まで</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[#6B5F54] leading-relaxed md:text-center">
                    小さなお子様の初めてのレッスンから、大人の趣味・再開レッスンまで対応しています。
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#E8E2D9] shadow-sm flex flex-col md:items-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#A88B58]/30">
                <div class="flex items-center md:flex-col md:text-center gap-3 mb-3 md:mb-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#A88B58]/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#A88B58] flex-shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 21l8.904-4.43m-8.904-.666L9 15.904m5.395-9.728L10 9.75m3.742.61l-3.535 3.535m7.879-8.964a1.902 1.902 0 112.689 2.689L6.75 21H3v-3.75L17.29 3.702z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-[#544A40] font-serif md:mt-2">初心者・経験者も相談可</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[#6B5F54] leading-relaxed md:text-center">
                    楽譜が読めない方、久しぶりに弾く方、基礎を見直したい方もご相談いただけます。
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#E8E2D9] shadow-sm flex flex-col md:items-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#A88B58]/30">
                <div class="flex items-center md:flex-col md:text-center gap-3 mb-3 md:mb-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#A88B58]/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#A88B58] flex-shrink-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m2.25 12 8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-[#544A40] font-serif md:mt-2">ご自宅・スタジオで受講</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-[#6B5F54] leading-relaxed md:text-center">
                    ご自宅のピアノ（電子ピアノ可）や近隣スタジオで受講いただけます。
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
